PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1771883655
OL,3,CNo retrial for boy accused of planning
OL,4,Cterror attack
OL,6,FBut the jury at Leeds Crown Court on 5
OL,7,FFebruary failed to reach a verdict on
OL,8,Fa more serious charge of preparing
OL,9,Facts of terrorism.
OL,11,FOn Monday (23 February), Michelle
OL,12,FHeeley KC confirmed to the judge, Mr
OL,13,FJustice Wall, that the prosecution
OL,14,Fwill not be seeking a retrial on this
OL,15,Fcharge.
OL,17,FThe judge said the teenager will now
OL,18,Fbe sentenced in Leeds on 27 March.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
