CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1771883655
OL,3,CNo retrial for boy accused of planning
OL,4,Cterror attack
OL,6,FThe jury was shown footage of the then
OL,7,F15-year-old practising firing a
OL,8,Fcrossbow Credit: Counter Terrorism
OL,9,FPolicing North East
OL,11,FThe boy's trial heard how police found
OL,12,Fan "arsenal" of weapons, including a
OL,13,Fcrossbow and knives, at his home in
OL,14,FNorthumberland in February 2025.
OL,16,FThe jury was shown images of his
OL,17,Fbedroom, including a replica of an SS
OL,18,Fofficer's cap, a flag of Rhodesia and
OL,19,Fa skeleton in a mask.
OL,26,@tD@DOUtD@LO]
