PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1771883655
OL,3,CNo retrial for boy accused of planning
OL,4,Cterror attack
OL,6,FJurors were also read online exchanges
OL,7,Fwith members of white supremacist
OL,8,Fgroups and violent journal entries.
OL,10,FThe court was told that the youth
OL,11,Fwatched a video of the New Zealand
OL,12,Fmosque terror attack then looked up
OL,13,Fsynagogues in the Newcastle area.
OL,15,FFrida Hussain KC, defending, told the
OL,16,Ftrial that the boy was "desperately
OL,17,Flonely", had been "plagued" with
OL,18,Fthoughts of killing himself, and
OL,19,Fcreated an online persona as a
OL,20,Fdistraction.
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@GO]yD@SOUyD@[O]
