OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1771883655
OL,3,CNo retrial for boy accused of planning
OL,4,Cterror attack
OL,6,FDuring the trial, Miss Hussain asked
OL,7,Fhim: "Writing in these terms about
OL,8,Fharming other people, was this
OL,9,Fanything you wanted to do in reality?"
OL,11,FThe defendant replied: "Just thoughts
OL,12,Fin my head. I never intended to harm
OL,13,Fanyone."
OL,26,@oD@FOUqD@fO]sD@XOUuD@HO]
